                <p class="card-text">You can build the application by following the steps in a series of tutorials.</p>
                <a href="https://docs.asp.net/en/latest/data/ef-mvc/intro.html" class="btn btn-primary">Go to tutorial</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm-6">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-body">
                <h5 class="card-title">Download it</h5>
                <p class="card-text">You can download the completed project from GitHub.</p>
                <a href="https://github.com/AndreMBarreira/university" class="btn btn-primary">Go to my Git</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>